Package: wdpar
Type: Package
Version: 0.0.0.1
Title: Interface to the World Database on Protected Areas
Description: Fetch and clean data from the World Database on Protected
    Areas (WDPA). Data is obtained from Protected Planet
    <http://protectedplanet.net>.
